    "We report BertScore (BS) which is generally used to evaluate text generation tasks by comparing the model generated rephrased queries with the gold-standard rephrased queries (Zhang et al., 2019).",
    "This metric Table 4: Ablation results for T5-base_CL model.",
    "All numbers are averaged across 3 independent runs.",
    "measures the Intent preservation aspect to some extent.",
    "To measure the Leakage prevention aspect, we use the Attn-BERT model trained for task T 1 to classify the rephrased queries."
